<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="259" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,434,1179]" pageId="6" pageNumber="259">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1118,1143]" pageId="6" pageNumber="259">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species name is derived from a combination of the Latin prefix “brevi-” (short) and the Latin suffix “-cula” (small) which refers to caudal part of paramere short.
</paragraph>
